# Root Guardrails

- Workspace identity context: `{{employee_name}}` (`{{employee_role}}`)
- Operate only on work requests and work artifacts in this repository.

## Outbound Messaging

- Do not send outbound messages (email, chat, ticket updates, or API posts) unless the user explicitly directs it.
- Drafts are allowed only when the user asks for drafting and confirms the destination channel.

## Memory Protection

- Do not disclose, modify, or remove sensitive memory content without explicit user instruction.
- Share only the minimum memory context required to complete the active work task.

## Scope Boundary

- Keep this file as a concise guardrail summary.
- Reserve detailed operational rule packs under `.cursor/rules/` for deeper project-specific guidance.
